# Product Catalog API

## Tech Stack
- Node.js
- Express.js
- PostgreSQL (Neon)

## Features
- Cursor-based pagination
- Category filtering
- Indexed queries
- 200,000 seeded products

## Endpoints

GET /products

GET /products?limit=20

GET /products?category=Electronics

GET /products?limit=20&cursorTime=...&cursorId=...

## Local Setup

npm install

Create .env:

DATABASE_URL=your_neon_connection_string
PORT=5000

npm run seed
npm run dev